Class StockModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.StockModel

  • public class StockModel
extends java.lang.Object
    StockModel is a class that gets and sets various stock information. The class includes functions:
    • get and set ticker
    • get and set stock exchange
    • get and set stock price
    • get and set last trade time
    • prints out all stock information

    Hyeun Kang
